  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of<strong> cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 15-20 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p>\n<p>Once cooked, drain and return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, peel the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot 'ribbons'</p>\n<p>Peel the<strong> cucumber</strong> into 'ribbons'</p>\n<p>Top, tail and slice the <strong>radishes </strong>as finely as you can</p>\n<p>Add the<strong> carrot ribbons</strong>,<strong> cucumber ribbons</strong> and <strong>sliced radishes</strong> to a large bowl – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the red <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1928.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
