            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil</strong>, <strong>lime juice</strong> and <strong>chopped chilli</strong> with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>Asian dressing</strong></p>",
